she is desperate for help

02:57.444 --> 02:59.144
and we should give it to her.

02:59.179 --> 03:00.845
Ask Pigeon what he thinks.

03:00.880 --> 03:02.981
-Where is he?
-MAN: Hey, man!

03:03.016 --> 03:03.982
