when we were vacuuming.

03:06.453 --> 03:09.888
I don't know if he's dead
or what, but he messed up
our vacuum cleaner pretty bad.

03:10.624 --> 03:12.624
Oh... (COUGHS)

03:15.495 --> 03:16.561
What happened?

03:16.596 --> 03:17.996
-He's fine.
-PIGEON: Oh!

03:18.031 --> 03:19.097
Yung, what do you think?

03:19.132 --> 03:21.066
(SNIFFLING)

03:21.101 --> 03:23.935
I, uh... I kinda think
this is more of a job
for a couples' counselor.

03:23.970 --> 03:27.572
Okay, so that's
a "no" from Yung,
a "yes" from Marquess,

03:27.607 --> 03:29.341
and an "abstained"
from Pigeon.

03:29.376 --> 03:31.610
So I guess
I'm the swing vote, huh?

03:31.645 --> 03:33.678
All that pressure, damn!

03:33.713 --> 03:35.013
Now I know what it feels like

03:35.048 --> 03:37.682
to be like Supreme Court
Justice Anthony Kennedy.

03:37.717 --> 03:40.619
All eyes on you.
Which way do you go?

03:40.654 --> 03:42.354
Which way do you go?

03:42.389 --> 03:44.856
(BREATHES DEEPLY)

03:46.393 --> 03:48.961
I guess I vote "yes!"

04:00.006 --> 04:02.173
Thanks for letting us
go in your car, lady,

04:02.208 --> 04:04.609
because it's like our car
just got cleaned.

04:04.644 --> 04:06.044
My car just got cleaned.

04:06.079 --> 04:07.846
Yeah, but I don't know
if you're a dirty person

04:07.881 --> 04:09.881
or you like to eat
in the car, you know?

04:09.916 --> 04:12.517
I am what they call
a clean freak.

04:13.953 --> 04:16.621
You mind if I look in here
and just poke around?

04:16.656 --> 04:19.691
