skin infection."

04:28.601 --> 04:30.836
Is yours moderate or severe?

04:33.006 --> 04:34.506
ANNE:
This is where Adam works.

04:34.541 --> 04:35.974
He's the produce manager.

04:37.410 --> 04:39.077
Yeah, there's no Adam here.

04:39.112 --> 04:41.980
