I've never seen that guy.

04:47.687 --> 04:49.487
I don't understand.

04:49.522 --> 04:51.156
Why would Adam lie to me?

04:52.926 --> 04:54.826
Sir, you're gonna have
to pay for that.

04:54.861 --> 04:58.029
Oh, um, I had this with me
when I came in.

04:58.064 --> 05:00.398
I brought this cereal with me
from my house.

05:00.433 --> 05:02.767
-Dad?
-Fine!

05:02.802 --> 05:04.936
Hey, lady, you got
another ten?

05:07.607 --> 05:08.907
Where would he go every day?

05:08.942 --> 05:11.509
Well, there's obviously
a lot more to the story.

05:11.544 --> 05:12.844
Not necessarily.

05:12.879 --> 05:15.013
This just might be
where the story ends.

05:15.048 --> 05:18.683
Unsatisfying,
unresolved, disturbing.

05:18.718 --> 05:20.151
Well, nice to meet you, ma'am.

05:20.186 --> 05:22.554
Can you give us a ride
back to the car wash?

05:22.589 --> 05:24.056
(ALL SCREAMING)

05:32.532 --> 05:33.932
