the United States Government.

07:42.128 --> 07:44.596
No! This is Adam's
and my baby.

07:44.631 --> 07:45.964
I don't care
what you say he is.

07:45.999 --> 07:47.398
He's the father of this child

07:47.433 --> 07:48.733
and we're going
to be a family!

07:48.768 --> 07:50.401
Oh, like C-3PO

07:50.436 --> 07:52.704
and his little baby, R2-D2.

07:52.739 --> 07:55.306
Take Anne to the clinic
for observation.

07:55.341 --> 07:57.475
-And kill the rest.
-MARQUESS: Kill?

07:57.510 --> 07:59.077
What the (BLEEP)?

07:59.979 --> 08:00.979
