08:21.834 --> 08:23.935
-Adam!
-Anne!

08:24.470 --> 08:25.737
ANNE: Mmm.

08:25.772 --> 08:27.438
Good thing he thought
we were Anne's friends.

08:27.473 --> 08:30.742
Uh, me next! (LAUGHS)
Kidding. Kinda.

